# Tsenta design system

Deliver token-driven, accessible UI for the Cosmo web client using Tsenta foundations.

## Intent

Structured, content-first marketing/product UI with semantic tokens, visible focus, and WCAG 2.2 AA contrast.

## Foundations (must)

- Use semantic CSS variables from `client/src/styles.css` (`--color-*`, `--font-*`, `--space-*`, `--radius-*`, `--shadow-*`, `--motion-*`).
- Do not hardcode one-off hex, spacing, or type sizes in components when a token exists.
- Font stack must remain Inter via `--font-family-stack`.
- Base type: `--font-size-base` / `--font-line-height-base`.
- Surfaces: dark shell (`--color-surface-base`) with light panels (`--color-surface-muted`).
- Primary CTA uses `--color-surface-strong`; raised/success accents use `--color-surface-raised`.

## Component states (must)

Every interactive control must define:

- default
- hover
- focus-visible (never remove outlines; use `--color-focus-ring`)
- active
- disabled
- loading (when async)
- error (when validation applies)

## Interaction (must)

- Keyboard-first: Tab order logical; Enter/Space activate buttons/links.
- Pointer and touch targets should be at least ~40px tall where practical.
- Links and buttons must have descriptive labels (no “Click here”).

## Content / overflow (should)

- Long titles clamp or wrap without breaking layout.
- Empty states use `.empty` and secondary text tokens.
- Prefer system density consistency over local visual exceptions.

## Accessibility acceptance criteria (must be testable)

- [ ] Focus-visible ring appears on keyboard focus for links, buttons, inputs, selects.
- [ ] Text on panels meets AA against `--color-surface-muted`.
- [ ] Text on dark shell meets AA against `--color-surface-base`.
- [ ] Disabled controls are not focusable for submit actions when invalid, or are clearly announced.
- [ ] Error text uses `--color-danger` and is associated with the field.

## Anti-patterns (must not)

- Low-contrast gray-on-gray text
- Hidden or outline:none focus without a replacement ring
- One-off spacing/type outside the token scale
- Ambiguous actions (“Submit”, “OK”) without context

## QA checklist

- [ ] No raw brand hex in new component CSS
- [ ] Primary buttons use `--color-surface-strong`
- [ ] Panels use `--color-surface-muted` + `--radius-xs` + `--shadow-2`
- [ ] Hover/focus/active/disabled verified
- [ ] Mobile toolbar/filters wrap without overflow
